[[ Class Exercise]]

Ex1
.In Application.js Make a function which returns the current date/time.
.Also make another function which returns the Date passed in a defined format.(“dd Month, yyyy HH:MM:ss”);

Ex2
.Make A Function which takes the “ID”, of the element and “HTML” as the parameter, And replaces the content of the element by the HTML supplied.

.Make a “div” on the Html Page with id=”timeDisp”. Write a function which uses all the functions developed in previous exercises to display current formatted time in the “div” created above.

Ex3
.Create an Object named Clock and encapsulate all functions in it.

Ex4
.Make an Interval which calls the method updateTime every one second.
Make a button which can stop this interval.
